text: Kris Jenner is ultimate bond girl at A-list 70th - but two stars didn't want to be seen
title: Latest news, views, pictures, video

meta_data.description: The mother to Kim Kardashian, Kris Jenner is an American reality television star. Kris has appeared on reality shows such as Keeping Up With The Kardashians, Kourtney and Kim Take Miami ,and Kourtney and Chole Take New York. She recently attended the National Television Awards in 2015.
